{"tid":710870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] Youtuber慢鏡捕捉超靚彩色渦旋","createTime":"2018-06-21T06:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T13:09:21.000Z","uid":138409,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31af9b170dccbfcbf62399cfd7c05e088f45fc92","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係高汁youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港大部分都<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYoutuber Smarter Everyday用四年時間複製經典實驗<br />\n<br />\nOriginal Research Paper by T. T. Lim &amp; T. B. Nickels (Published in Nature 1992)<br />\nhttp://202.118.74.190/~elizabeth/Docs...<br />\n<br />\n用慢鏡拍攝顏料渦旋碰撞後形成的花紋<br />\n最終結果賞心悅目<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EVbdbVhzcM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEVbdbVhzcM4&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=22d19a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EVbdbVhzcM4</a><br />\n<br />\n12小時足本版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cm9l8-qngjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCm9l8-qngjM&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0a46e5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cm9l8-qngjM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/135450_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F135450_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif&h=40d85e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/140116_2f9d087bb585505730bb811219e9fb9a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F140116_2f9d087bb585505730bb811219e9fb9a.gif&h=83bae6a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f44ebb106ac0e34f84053be90c590d93ab9011cf","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203424cb2ac20b7f8fdf0e24864b1396a0492a18","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47fce43cfeb4fa3c99206808213947062f8c919","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d994a0ddaea32af1db8b50238aee326fa0c9911c","tid":710870,"uid":139674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc348d1a3801af96d73cc37382c0288441a87759","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8507b51b5fc39e96925141d10f24e4763790f09","tid":710870,"uid":185953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c273d6e4c4bcd412ed0702d02bf145751d7b179","tid":710870,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"原本個實驗係講咩？"},{"pid":"4d48d7985377c918e8264cc5d59520b78b9fc1eb","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"以下為原作者在Youtube的簡介，內容主要是供有興趣了解更多的人查閱的資料<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\nGET SMARTER SECTION<br />\n<br />\n維基百科中有關「渦旋」的條目<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vortex_ring\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FVortex_ring&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=66dddd67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vortex_ring</a><br />\n<br />\n1992年出版的科學論文，作者為Dr. T T Lim，內容為探討這個現象<br />\nhttp://202.118.74.190/~elizabeth/Docs/34_Instability_Head-on%20collision_of_large_VR.pdf<br />\n<br />\n流體動力學公式<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eng.auburn.edu/~tplacek/courses/fluidsreview-1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eng.auburn.edu%2F~tplacek%2Fcourses%2Ffluidsreview-1.pdf&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c5f539b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.eng.auburn.edu/~tplacek/courses/fluidsreview-1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n此現象之數值分析<br />\n<a href=\"http://fluid.itcmp.pwr.wroc.pl/~znmp/Publikacje/JP_2014_Kudela_Kosior.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffluid.itcmp.pwr.wroc.pl%2F~znmp%2FPublikacje%2FJP_2014_Kudela_Kosior.pdf&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ef3f3e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fluid.itcmp.pwr.wroc.pl/~znmp/Publikacje/JP_2014_Kudela_Kosior.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有關渦旋圈重新連接的有趣論文<br />\n<a href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/3721/e67f5bf8e88a47e2241058c7e3cc064c5e8a.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpdfs.semanticscholar.org%2F3721%2Fe67f5bf8e88a47e2241058c7e3cc064c5e8a.pdf&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a08cb692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/3721/e67f5bf8e88a47e2241058c7e3cc064c5e8a.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nDr. T T Lim拍攝的其他影片<br />\n<a href=\"http://me.nus.edu.sg/dept/limtt/videogallery.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fme.nus.edu.sg%2Fdept%2Flimtt%2Fvideogallery.html&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f26355f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://me.nus.edu.sg/dept/limtt/videogallery.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFlow Visualization, 由 Dr. T T Lim寫的一本書<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Flow-Visualization-Techniques-Examples-Second/dp/1848167911/ref=mt_hardcover?_encoding=UTF8&amp;me=&amp;qid=1529505335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFlow-Visualization-Techniques-Examples-Second%2Fdp%2F1848167911%2Fref%3Dmt_hardcover%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26me%3D%26qid%3D1529505335&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0d8614bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Flow-Visualization-Techniques-Examples-Second/dp/1848167911/ref=mt_hardcover?_encoding=UTF8&amp;me=&amp;qid=1529505335</a><br />\n<br />\n為何在流體我們通常不談角動量<br />\n<a href=\"https://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/127712/why-dont-we-talk-about-angular-momentum-at-all-in-fluid-mechanics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphysics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F127712%2Fwhy-dont-we-talk-about-angular-momentum-at-all-in-fluid-mechanics&d=7KHW35M%2FDTk2%2Be6291MzfgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=eaf5a727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/127712/why-dont-we-talk-about-angular-momentum-at-all-in-fluid-mechanics</a>"},{"pid":"4ec0b23b6103d82af9c161becc8d24ffe41aa090","tid":710870,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c273d6e4c4bcd412ed0702d02bf145751d7b179","tid":710870,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"原本個實驗係講咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"探討一種名為「渦旋」的現象，特別係當兩個渦旋撞埋一齊時會點<br />\n有興趣的話可以參考個youtuber比嘅參考資料（#9）"},{"pid":"3871c2b937507e365ba351d5d6fa6b1d49d6b225","tid":710870,"uid":3932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T13:09:21.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n做FYP reference"}]}